flowchart_mermaid:
flowchart TD
  A[Idle interval] --> B{Automation enabled?}
  B -- no --> Z[Stop]
  B -- yes --> C[Scan Kanban automatically]
  C --> D{Item or ancestor automation_excluded?}
  D -- yes --> X[Skip/cancel branch markers]
  D -- no --> E[Review Processor]
  D -- no --> F[Preprocessing Processor]
  E --> G{Review text exists and source changed?}
  G -- no --> H[No review work]
  G -- yes --> I[Queue/process review marker with local AI]
  F --> J{Open ordinary leaf in ToDo lane?}
  J -- no --> K[No preprocessing work]
  J -- yes --> L{Readiness marker missing or stale?}
  L -- no --> M[No preprocessing work]
  L -- yes --> N[Queue/process preprocessing marker with local AI]
  N --> O{Result}
  O -- ready --> P[Write readiness marker]
  O -- decomposition --> Q[Create/confirm children and move parent out of ToDo]
  O -- blocked/question --> R[Create visible blocker/question]
